        <item>
            <title>1.9.1</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 12:56:30 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>32</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.9.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Fixed Swift 6 strict concurrency violation in window close key monitor
- Fixed window close detection using actual session state instead of fragile window title check
- Fixed SSH reconnecting windows being closed instead of hidden
- Removed dead code from force-close path cleanup
- Restored proper keyboard shortcut display on "Close and Stop Session" menu item
]]></description>
