        <item>
            <title>1.9.0</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 11:40:15 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>31</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.9.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features
- **Background sessions**: Closing a window (×/Cmd+W) now hides it instead of terminating the session. Sessions like `/loop` and `/remote-control` continue running in the background
- **Reopen hidden windows**: Click the Dock icon to bring back all hidden windows with their sessions intact
- **Force close**: Use Option+Cmd+W or "Close and Stop Session" from the File menu to fully close a window and terminate its session
- **Quit confirmation**: Cmd+Q now shows a confirmation dialog when active sessions are running, preventing accidental session loss
]]></description>
